OL,3,CMan jailed after police find two
OL,4,Cfirearms and huge stockpile of illegal
OL,5,Cdrugs
OL,7,FA who was found with two firearms and
OL,8,Fa huge stockpile of illegal drugs in
OL,9,FKent has been jailed for six years.
OL,11,FOn 27 July 2023, officers carried out
OL,12,Fa warrant at an industrial estate near
OL,13,FBethersden after David Allen was seen
OL,14,Fapproaching the site in his van.
OL,16,FHe was arrested and a container he had
OL,17,Fthe keys to was searched. Inside
OL,18,Fofficers found more than 60 kilos of
OL,19,Famphetamine, more than a kilo of
OL,20,Fcocaine and around #70,000 in cash.
