OL,3,CMan jailed after police find two
OL,4,Cfirearms and huge stockpile of illegal
OL,5,Cdrugs
OL,7,FAlso discovered were two small guns,
OL,8,Fwhich Allen claimed were antiques, but
OL,9,Fwhich were later found to be viable.
OL,11,FDetectives also found drug packaging,
OL,12,Fmoney counting machines, needles and
OL,13,Fsyringes and a purity test for cocaine.
OL,15,FAt his home nearby, police seized 25
OL,16,Fdesigner watches, ledgers recording
OL,17,Fdeals, as well as a CS spray and a
OL,18,Fknuckleduster.
