OL,3,CMan jailed after police find two
OL,4,Cfirearms and huge stockpile of illegal
OL,5,Cdrugs
OL,7,FFurther examination later estimated
OL,8,Fthe drugs' street value at around
OL,9,F#500,000.
OL,11,FAllen, of Green Lane, Marden, was
OL,12,Fcharged with and later admitted
OL,13,Fpossessing amphetamine and cocaine
OL,14,Fwith intent to supply, three charges
OL,15,Fof possession of a prohibited firearm
OL,16,Fand possessing criminal property.
OL,18,FThe 54-year-old was brought before
OL,19,FMaidstone Crown Court on Wednesday (31
OL,20,FJanuary 2024) and jailed for six years.
