OL,4,Cfirearms and huge stockpile of illegal
OL,5,Cdrugs
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Stacey Chapman, of
OL,8,Fthe Kent and Essex Serious Crime
OL,9,FDirectorate, said: "Our officers have
OL,10,Fseized a large amount of class-A
OL,11,Fdrugs, which would have profited
OL,12,Fcriminal networks and led to further
OL,13,Fcrime and more offences.
OL,15,F"The weapons we found illustrate all
OL,16,Fto clearly the violence, or threat of
OL,17,Fviolence, which goes hand in hand with
OL,18,Fdrug dealing, and I am pleased those
OL,19,Fweapons have been taken off the
OL,20,Fstreets.
